{"actor":"charly vibes","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T14:57:14Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":79,"issue_id":"fotos-15o","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"fotos-15o\",\"title\":\"Support multi-language OCR (fra/deu/spa tessdata download)\",\"description\":\"The ai-processing spec requires OCR language support beyond English. After eng.traineddata is bundled (fotos-e47), add: a language selector in the AI settings panel (dropdown: English, French, German, Spanish); on-demand tessdata download from tessdata GitHub releases to app data directory; download progress indicator; language preference persisted to settings. The run_ocr() command must accept an optional lang parameter (default 'eng') and pass it to Tesseract initialization. Depends on fotos-e47 (tessdata bundling).\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"charly.vibes@proton.me\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-23T23:28:41Z\",\"created_by\":\"charly vibes\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-23T23:28:41Z\"}"}
{"actor":"charly vibes","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T14:57:27Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":80,"issue_id":"fotos-15o","new_value":"{\"status\":\"open\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"fotos-15o\",\"title\":\"Support multi-language OCR (fra/deu/spa tessdata download)\",\"description\":\"The ai-processing spec requires OCR language support beyond English. After eng.traineddata is bundled (fotos-e47), add: a language selector in the AI settings panel (dropdown: English, French, German, Spanish); on-demand tessdata download from tessdata GitHub releases to app data directory; download progress indicator; language preference persisted to settings. The run_ocr() command must accept an optional lang parameter (default 'eng') and pass it to Tesseract initialization. Depends on fotos-e47 (tessdata bundling).\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"charly.vibes@proton.me\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-23T23:28:41Z\",\"created_by\":\"charly vibes\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T17:57:15Z\"}"}
{"actor":"charly vibes","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T16:45:45Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":81,"issue_id":"fotos-33s","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"fotos-33s\",\"title\":\"Implement trackpad pinch-to-zoom\",\"description\":\"The canvas engine handles Ctrl+wheel for trackpad pinch but native pinch gesture events (GestureEvent on Safari, or ctrlKey+wheel on Chrome/WebView2) may not be fully handled on all platforms. Verify and implement: detect pinch via wheel event with ctrlKey=true and deltaMode=0 (pixel mode); compute zoom centered on pinch midpoint; prevent default to stop OS zoom. Test on Wayland with libinput trackpad. Should use the same cursor-centered zoom math as mouse wheel.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":4,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"charly.vibes@proton.me\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-23T23:23:01Z\",\"created_by\":\"charly vibes\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-23T23:23:01Z\"}"}
